  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Alone in the Stars: Survivor is an action rogue-lite where you destroy hordes of aliens and bosses using custom load-outs and synergies between power-ups. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In this third-person shooter, harness the power of deep customization—choose your stats, abilities, weapons, and upgrade paths to create unstoppable synergies. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/d61921de34f5a692172be289088088ae.poster.avif?t=1757345784\" width=614 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/d61921de34f5a692172be289088088ae.webm?t=1757345784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/d61921de34f5a692172be289088088ae.mp4?t=1757345784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIND OVERPOWERED SYNERGIES BETWEEN POWERUPS</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All power-ups stack and scale infinitely. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Synergize different power-ups together with different elemental effects, explosions, on hit, on shoot, and many more unique effects. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unique utility abilities and 4 damage abilities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match different pools of power-ups to find your preferred builds. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/0a1c92ac85e4fa60d334ab7805a250b4.poster.avif?t=1757345784\" width=614 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/0a1c92ac85e4fa60d334ab7805a250b4.webm?t=1757345784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/0a1c92ac85e4fa60d334ab7805a250b4.mp4?t=1757345784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY YOUR WAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mix together and build your own character to match your play style with:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 guns & 1 sword to pick from.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely change your base stats and equip unique passive abilities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 unique utility abilities and 4 damage abilities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the pool of power-ups available to you in a run.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize the look of your alien before each run. Change body types, colors, and more. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PROGRESS EVERY RUN</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new power-ups, passives, abilities, weapons, levels, and cosmetics. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/ce8acebada3545ec5ad3e8e520f7446b.poster.avif?t=1757345784\" width=614 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/ce8acebada3545ec5ad3e8e520f7446b.webm?t=1757345784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/ce8acebada3545ec5ad3e8e520f7446b.mp4?t=1757345784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DIFFERENT EVERY RUN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It'll feel different every time you play with:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 planets, unique enemies for every planet, and different layouts of each planet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 elite emotional variants of every enemy. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ power-ups to find different synergies with.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random weapons in each run.   </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Alone in the Stars: Survivor is an action rogue-lite where you destroy hordes of aliens and bosses using custom load-outs and synergies between power-ups. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In this third-person shooter, harness the power of deep customization—choose your stats, abilities, weapons, and upgrade paths to create unstoppable synergies. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/d61921de34f5a692172be289088088ae.poster.avif?t=1757345784\" width=614 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/d61921de34f5a692172be289088088ae.webm?t=1757345784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/d61921de34f5a692172be289088088ae.mp4?t=1757345784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIND OVERPOWERED SYNERGIES BETWEEN POWERUPS</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All power-ups stack and scale infinitely. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Synergize different power-ups together with different elemental effects, explosions, on hit, on shoot, and many more unique effects. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unique utility abilities and 4 damage abilities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match different pools of power-ups to find your preferred builds. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/0a1c92ac85e4fa60d334ab7805a250b4.poster.avif?t=1757345784\" width=614 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478310/extras/0a1c92ac85e4fa