agraph\" >5 planets, unique enemies for every planet, and different layouts of each planet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 elite emotional variants of every enemy. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ power-ups to find different synergies with.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random weapons in each run.   </p></li></ul>",
